      "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\nthe patch was very close to pass with zfs :)\n\nLU-2561 newly created file is same size as directory...\n[3] $ mkdir -p 2561 -- ok\n[4] $ cd 2561 -- ok\n[5] $ getfacl --access . | setfacl -d -M- . -- ok\n[6] $ touch f1 -- ok\n[7] $ ls -s f1 -- failed\n0 f1                                  ? 1 f1                                   \n[9] $ rm -rf 2561 -- ok\n6 commands (5 passed, 1 failed)\n sanity test_103: @@@@@@ FAIL: LU-2561 test failed",
